{"tid":2379221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（推）中国新增\"肛拭子\"检测，华人亲历：全程羞耻。","createTime":"2021-01-25T05:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T16:42:05.000Z","uid":330057,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"9e603d439e1b7609c7b8d80e83c253c118ccebce","tid":2379221,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:48:01.000Z","msg":"【#新冠核酸檢測為何增加肛拭子採樣#？】日前，北京大興區感染病例所在區域人員均進行了咽拭子、肛拭子和血清檢測。專家表示，研究發現一部分感染者糞便或肛拭子核酸陽性持續時間比上呼吸道持續時間更長，#增加肛拭子採樣可提高檢出率減少漏診#；但肛拭子採樣不夠便捷，目前只對隔離點等重點人群使用。 <a href=\"http://t.cn/A65bVFsx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.cn%2FA65bVFsx&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=c055ea39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.cn/A65bVFsx</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/2656274875/4596430163939628\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2F2656274875%2F4596430163939628&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=5b52e08e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/2656274875/4596430163939628</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oE4itDW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoE4itDW.png&h=4d418d51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pq6Ec5C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPq6Ec5C.png&h=cd250bf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08c7c2f22e5a9e532a88ddb7163739d12cc76fe4","tid":2379221,"uid":330057,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:49:40.000Z","msg":"我國在肛門探索的領域上又再次領先<br />\n而家冇試過肛𢫨子，搵條野插落個肛門到係咁撩<br />\n都唔算係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"62e2071e2b20363437a3d2da19ca78c127f1858a","tid":2379221,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"冇人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0b854be880d31b58baf46e4cd9f9b1559cf9d8","tid":2379221,"uid":253016,"